ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurse
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecursePlusAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseTypePredicated
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseTypePredicatedPlusAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseAttributes
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendant 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is *NOT* 'HtmlAttributes' (no recursion).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteInputObjPlusAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' irregardless of its type (no recursion).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the direct descendants, *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the direct descendants, including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAtDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all descendants at the specified depth from 'InputObject', *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAtDepthInclAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all descendants at the specified depth from 'InputObject', including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s) (no recursion).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedOrAttribInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s) (no recursion).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the direct descendants that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'HtmlAttributes' of the 'InputObject', if present, along with the direct descendants that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedAtDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all descendants at the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedAtDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all descendants at the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' at that depth.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'HtmlAttributes' of the 'InputObject', if present.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesAtDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all descendant 'HtmlAttributes' at the specified depth from 'InputObject'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteInputObjAndDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is *NOT* 'HtmlAttributes', along with all direct descendants, *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteInputObjAttribAndDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject', along with all direct descendants, including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedInputObjAndDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all direct descendants that match the specified type(s), irregardless of whether the 'InputObject' was a match.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedInputObjAndDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s), along with the 'HtmlAttributes' of the 'InputObject' and all direct descendants that match the specified type(s), irregardless of whether the 'InputObject' was a match.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesInputObjOrDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes'; otherwise the 'HtmlAttributes' of the 'InputObject' is returned, if present.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is *NOT* 'HtmlAttributes', along with all recursive descendants, *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseInclAttribAndInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' along with all recursive descendants, including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseTypePredicatedInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants that match the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseTypePredicatedInclInputObjAndAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants that match the specified type(s), along with all descendant 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseAttribInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes'; otherwise all recursive descendant 'HtmlAttributes' will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteFromDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject', *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteFromDepthInclAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject', including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedFromDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedFromDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' from that depth.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesFromDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendant 'HtmlAttributes' starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteToDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants up to the specified depth from 'InputObject', *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteToDepthInclAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match the specified single type, along with all 'HtmlAttributes' to that depth.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteToDepthInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is *NOT* 'HtmlAttributes', along with all recursive descendants up to the specified depth, *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteToDepthInclAttribAndInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' along with all recursive descendants up to the specified depth, including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedToDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedToDepthInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth, that match the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedToDepthInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth, that match the specified type(s), along with all descendant 'HtmlAttributes' up to that depth.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedToDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' to that depth.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesToDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendant 'HtmlAttributes' up to the specified depth from 'InputObject'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesToDepthInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes'; otherwise all recursive descendant 'HtmlAttributes' up to the specified depth will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteInRange
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants within the specified depth range from 'InputObject', *NOT* including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteInRangeInclAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants within the specified depth range from 'InputObject', including 'HtmlAttributes'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedInRange
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, within the specified depth range from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s).

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttribAndTypePredicatedInRange
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, within the specified depth range from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' within that range.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteAttributesInRange
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendant 'HtmlAttributes' within the specified depth range from 'InputObject'.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatched
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants that match any of the specified type(s). No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedPlusAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes'. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants that match the specified type(s). No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedInclInputObjOrAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants that match the specified type(s), along with all descendant 'HtmlAttributes'. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedFromDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s). No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedFromDepthOrAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, starting from the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' from that depth. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedToDepth
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s). No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedToDepthOrAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' to that depth. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedToDepthInclInputObjOrAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth, that match the specified type(s). No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedPlusAttribToDepthInclInputObj
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all recursive descendants, up to the specified depth, that match the specified type(s), along with all descendant 'HtmlAttributes' up to that depth. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedInRange
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, within the specified depth range from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s). No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteRecurseUnmatchedOrAttribInRange
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns all recursive descendants, within the specified depth range from 'InputObject' that match any of the specified type(s), along with all 'HtmlAttributes' within that range. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedInputObjOrDirectDesc
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it matches any of the specified type(s), along with all direct descendants that match the specified type(s), irregardless of whether the 'InputObject' was a match. No descendants of matches will be returned.

ProcessRecordMethods.Name: WriteTypePredicatedInputObjDirectDescOrAttrib
ProcessRecordMethods.Description: Returns the 'InputObject' if it is 'HtmlAttributes' or it matches any of the specified type(s); otherwise, the 'HtmlAttributes' of the 'InputObject' if it exists, along with all direct descendants that match the specified type(s).
